title: From SNL to SMD...
itunes:title: From SNL to SMD...
description:
TUE 10/25 - Comedian Pete Davidson joins The Breakfast Club to talk about SNL's success during this election season, his new Comedy Central special "SMD" (in honor of his father's initials) and why he says Kid Cudi saved his life...but Lil' Yachty is ruining it.
